<p class="lead">A custom marquee component that smoothly scrolls its child elements.</p>
<p class="lead">This component is designed to loop elements horizontally within a container, with support for customization such as speed, gap, pause on hover, and more.</p>

<hr class="my-4">

<div class="js-marquee">
  <h2 class="m-0">With Text</h2>

  <div class="py-3 d-flex flex-row justify-content-start align-items-center gap-1">
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary js-play">Play</button>

    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary js-pause">Pause</button>

    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary js-render">Manual Render</button>
  </div>

  <div class="js-marquee" style="font-size: 2rem;" data-gap="20" data-pause-on-hover="true">Marquee</div>
</div>

<hr class="my-4">

<div class="js-marquee">
  <h2 class="m-0">With Reverse Speed</h2>

  <div class="py-3 d-flex flex-row justify-content-start align-items-center gap-1">
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary js-play">Play</button>

    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary js-pause">Pause</button>

    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary js-render">Manual Render</button>
  </div>

  <div class="js-marquee" style="font-size: 2rem;" data-gap="20" data-pause-on-hover="true" data-speed="-1">Marquee</div>
</div>

<hr class="my-4">

<div class="js-marquee">
  <h2 class="m-0">With HTML</h2>

  <div class="py-3 d-flex flex-row justify-content-start align-items-center gap-1">
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary js-play">Play</button>

    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary js-pause">Pause</button>

    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary js-render">Manual Render</button>
  </div>

  <div class="js-marquee" style="font-size: 3rem;" data-gap="10" data-speed="3">
    <div style="background-color: #dd7171; height: 100px; width: 20vw"></div>
    <div style="background-color: #32e3d7; height: 100px; width: 10vw"></div>
    <div style="background-color: #5139d7; height: 10px; width: 15vw"></div>
    <div style="background-color: #e332d4; height: 100px; width: 5vw"></div>
    <div style="background-color: #000; height: 100px; width: 50vw"></div>
  </div>
</div>

